headline: ‘This team is guided by science’: Kenvue chief hits back at Trump and RFK Jr.’s Tylenol autism claims in memo to 20,000 employees
summary: Promotion of unproven claims from President Trump and RFK Jr. linking acetaminophen (Tylenol) to autism have significantly impacted Kenvue’s business.
